  @NegativeTest @skipGrammarCheck
  Scenario: [12] Fail on an incomplete hexadecimal integer
    Given any graph
    When executing query:
      """
      RETURN 0x AS literal
      """
    Then a SyntaxError should be raised at compile time: InvalidNumberLiteral

